Failed to connect the Internet to get information on the update. Possible reasons: 

• There is no connection to the Internet; 
• 1C website is temporarily unavailable; 
• The firewall or other middleware (antiviruses, etc.) blocks the attempt of the application to connect to Internet;
• The connection to the Internet is established through a proxy server, but its parameters are not configured in the application.
